sequenceDiagram
  %% 1回の memory query シーケンス図: 1回の問い合わせで何が順に起きるか

  actor Human as 人 / AI agent
  participant Tool as memory workflow
  participant Lens as SearchLens / RetrievalPolicy
  participant Policy as ObjectiveRoutePolicy
  participant Routes as Route Portfolio
  participant Guard as ProviderApiBudgetGuard
  participant Evidence as Source Bundle / Context / Citation
  participant Authority as AnswerAuthorityGatekeeper
  participant Boundary as Answer Boundary
  participant Trace as 実行記録

  Human->>Tool: 質問を渡す
  Tool->>Trace: sidecar trace を開始する
  Tool->>Lens: 関心・重み・探索姿勢を確認する
  Lens->>Policy: 検索方針を渡す
  Policy->>Routes: 候補ルートを選ぶ

  par ローカル候補ルート
    Routes-->>Tool: local candidates
  and provider-backed ルート
    Routes->>Guard: 実行可否と予算を確認する
    alt 承認済み
      Guard-->>Routes: provider candidates
      Routes-->>Tool: provider-backed candidates
    else freeze / 予算不明
      Guard-->>Trace: provider_gated を記録する
      Guard-->>Tool: provider_gated skip
    end
  end

  Tool->>Evidence: candidate を source bundle に戻す
  Evidence->>Evidence: context chunk と citation を作る
  Evidence->>Authority: claim support を判定する
  alt 回答に使える
    Authority-->>Boundary: answer support
    Boundary-->>Tool: answer
  else 復元・引用・主張支えが不足
    Authority-->>Boundary: source_not_restored / citation_missing / hypothesis_only / needs_review
    Boundary-->>Tool: stop status
  end
  Tool->>Trace: route / guard / evidence / stop reason を記録する
  Tool-->>Human: Answer Boundary status と citations を返す
